Use this template to reference a specific user: 
<nowiki>{{</nowiki>'''User'''|''Username''<nowiki>}}</nowiki>
For example:
<nowiki>{{</nowiki>User|Petert<nowiki>}}</nowiki> will appear as 
{{en/User|Petert}} with a link to his user page. </noinclude>
